<promed@promedmail.org>
[An official confirmation -- or otherwise -- of the above outbreak and of
the alleged other recent outbreaks in South Africa will be useful. South
Africa's last notification to the OIE on an outbreak of NCD was
received on 2 December 2004 (see
<http://oie.int/eng/info/hebdo/AIS_16.HTM#Sec11>); a total of 4 outbreaks
were recorded during Oct-Dec 2004. - Mod.AS].
